<paragraph id="P-0021" lvl="7"><number>&lsqb;0021&rsqb;</number> because by doing so, signal R<highlight><subscript>1 </subscript></highlight>contains as much information about c<highlight><subscript>1</subscript></highlight><highlight><superscript>1</superscript></highlight>, i&equals;1, 2, 3, . . . n as is possible. However, it can be easily shown that if a matrix A is constructed such that  
